os MORI </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:9pt">for BBC, 2,078 adults 15+, 2012</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn61"></a><a href="#_ftnref61">[61]</a><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:9pt">  </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:9pt">Ipsos MORI for the BBC, 2,118 UK adults 15+, June 2013</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn62"></a><a href="#_ftnref62">[62]</a><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:9pt"> Based on 2013 Licence Fee income</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn63"></a><a href="#_ftnref63">[63]</a><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:9pt"> </span><a href="http://www.bbc.co.uk/aboutthebbc/insidethebbc/howwework/reports/bbc_report_public_and_private_broadcasting.html"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Calibri; font-size:9pt; text-decoration:underline">Public and Private Broadcasters Round t</span><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Calibri; font-size:9pt; text-decoration:underline">he World – A Race to the Top</span></a><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:9pt"> </span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn64"></a><a href="#_ftnref64">[64]</a><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:9pt"> </span><a href="http://www.bbc.co.uk/bbctrust/news/press_releases/2013/governance_review.html"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Calibri; font-size:9pt; text-decoration:underline">Review of BBC internal governance</span></a><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:9pt">, December 2013</span></p></body></html>